The film has received mixed reviews, with some critics praising its charming animation and sweet story, while others criticized it as being overstuffed and unoriginal. One article notes that Curtis's previous film, "Love Actually," is referenced in "That Christmas," while another article highlights the casting of Brian Cox as Santa Claus. The titles also provide information about the film's release date (2024) and its availability on Netflix.
